form.name: Defect/Bug/Issue Report
form.description: The following fields are all required to process this report. Enter 'N/A' in fields that are not applicable.

field.name: Summary Information
field.description: Restate the problem title and/or include more descriptive summary information.

field.name: Steps to Reproduce
field.description: Include any setup or preparation work and the steps we can take to reproduce the problem.

field.name: Results
field.description: Describe your results and how they differed from what you expected.

field.name: Regression
field.description: Provide information on steps taken to isolate the problem. Under what conditions or circumstances does the problem occur or not occur.

field.name: Workaround
field.description: If there is a workaround for the problem, please describe it in detail.

field.name: Documentation & Notes
field.description: Document any additional information that might be useful in resolving the problem.

field.name: State
field.options: ["","Alabama","Alaska","Arkansas","Arizona","California","Colorado","Connecticut","Delaware","Florida","Georgia","Hawaii","Idaho","Illinois","Indiana","Iowa","Kansas","Kentucky","Louisiana","Maine","Maryland","Massachusetts","Michigan","Minnesota","Mississippi","Missouri","Montana","Nebraska","Nevada","New Hampshire","New Jersey","New Mexico","New York","North Carolina","North Dakota","Ohio","Oklahoma","Oregon","Pennsylvania","Rhode Island","South Carolina","South Dakota","Tennessee","Texas","Utah","Vermont","Virginia","Washington","West Virginia","Wisconsin","Wyoming"]

field.name: Main Photo URL
field.description: If using a photo that is already online, you can insert the URL here.

field.name: Main Photo Upload
field.description: Or if you would like to upload the photo, this would be a good spot.

field.name: NextGen Gallery ID
field.description: If you would like to post a Photo Gallery, insert the NextGen gallery ID for this home here.

field.options: ["Balcony","BBQ","Courtyard","Horse Facilities","Greenhouse","Lease Option","Pets Allowed","RV\/Boat Parking","Spa\/Hot Tub","Tennis Court(s)"]
